entry.title: Physton/sd-webui-prompt-all-in-one
entry.summary: This is an extension based on sd-webui, aimed at improving the user experience of the prompt/negative prompt input box. It has a more intuitive and powerful input interface function, and provides automatic translation, history record, and bookmarking functions. 这是一个基于 sd-webui 的扩展，旨在提高提示词/反向提示词输入框的使用体验。它拥有更直观、强大的输入界面功能，它提供了自动翻译、历史记录和收藏等功能。
